          "ins_item_num": 5,
          "ins_total": 594.29,
          "f9": "Our line item covers insurance line 5. We are requesting 280.42 LF of Asphalt Starter - universal starter course.\n\n1. Per Xactimate pricing, this costs $580.47. The insurance report shows 280.39 LF; we are using the EagleView-confirmed drip edge perimeter of 280.42 LF.\n\na. Starter is a distinct roofing component with a separate material profile and a higher associated labor rate compared to field shingles. As such, it should not be included within waste calculations for field shingles, as doing so results in inaccurate material and labor estimates. A review of the corresponding Xactimate line item details will confirm that starter installation is priced at a higher labor rate, reflecting the specialized nature of its application at roof edges.\n\nb. If this was standard practice to include starter in the waste across the industry, then the separate line item in Xactimate would not exist.\n\nc. Please see attached EagleView for measurements.",
